# Kit-internal bookkeeping that should NOT be published to the kit's public GitHub repo.
# These files live in this folder for convenience (so they sit next to the kit they describe),
# but they're meta-records about the kit's own lifecycle, not template content for downstream apps.

# Records every sync of process improvements from the upstream Engage planning workflow
# into this kit. Engage-internal bookkeeping; not useful or appropriate for public consumption.
STARTER-KIT-SYNC-LOG.md

